# Canonical URL enforcement — 301 all alternate URLs to https://waxlashtan.com
# Prevents GSC "Alternate page with proper canonical tag" by not serving duplicates

# www → apex
https://www.waxlashtan.com https://waxlashtan.com 301
https://www.waxlashtan.com/ https://waxlashtan.com 301
https://www.waxlashtan.com/* https://waxlashtan.com/:splat 301

# Trailing-slash root → canonical (no trailing slash)
https://waxlashtan.com/ https://waxlashtan.com 301

# /index.html duplicate → canonical root
/index.html / 301
